  "summary": "Main\nBy Jeffrey Landsberg\nIndia produced approximately 144.4 billion kilowatt hours of electricity last month. This is up month-on-month by 8.6 billion kilowatt hours (6%), up year-on-year by 17.8 billion kilowatt hours (14%), and is a record. The 14% year-on-year growth also marks the largest growth seen all year.",
